title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football Reaction, Matt Ryan
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football Reaction, Matt Ryan
description:
Dan reacts to last night's Monday Night Football game and the overtime win by the Los Angeles Chargers. And he talks to Indianapolis Colts QB Matt Ryan about his transition to a new team after 14 years with the Atlanta Falcons.
